Class ProcessGroup

java.lang.Object
  com.orbitz.monitoring.lib.factory.ProcessGroup

@ManagedResource(description="ProcessGroup can be enabled/disabled and MonitoringLevel adjusted")
public class ProcessGroup
extends java.lang.Object

An object that contains the configuration for what processors should be called for which monitors.
